title: ‘Atlanta’ Season 4, Episode 9
description:
Charles and Van go deep into the countryside as they breakdown Alfred’s wild hog-filled, tractor-ridden adventure and what this solo journey means for the development of the character.
Hosts: Charles Holmes and Van Lathan
Associate Producer: Jonathan Kermah
